                    <summary>Notes on the lectures of John Hunter, with the body of the lecture text on the recto, and notes on the verso of the pages. The substance of the lectures has been 
                        epitomized into a series of 1758 numbered aphorisms.</summary>
                   
                    <textLang mainLang="en" source="IANA">English</textLang>
                    
